# Design System Harness

For `src/components/` work, follow [CODEX.md](../../CODEX.md):

- 1 component = 4 files (tsx, types, stories, index)
- Colors: `var(--color-*)` / Tailwind theme tokens — no `#hex` in components
- Width: `w-full` + parent padding — no fixed `w-[NNNpx]`
- Figma variants only — no invented props
- Approval required before first write (see `.codex/CODEX.md`)

Subagents: `.codex/agents/figma-implementer.md`, `token-checker.md`, `design-qa.md`, `design-reviewer.md`
